query:
INSERT INTO transportation (tripId, type, flightNumber, origin, destination, departureDate, arrivalDate, confirmationNumber, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes, company, carModel, pickupLocation, returnLocation, phone, linkedDocumentId, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 2 as tripId, type, flightNumber, origin, destination, departureDate, arrivalDate, confirmationNumber, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes, company, carModel, pickupLocation, returnLocation, phone, linkedDocumentId, NOW() as createdAt, NOW() as updatedAt
FROM transportation
WHERE tripId = 1;
